PrecisAuthorization for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant an EASEMENT (ES-939) to CLARIDGE HOMES (RIVERSIDE) INC. encumbering, in perpetuity or for the term of the use of the works or any replacement thereof, a small piece of land on the east side of Colonel By Drive in Ottawa, Ontario, for the purposes of a water main serving its Kings Landing housing development.
